data.value: <color=0,0,0><size=+5>What is Precious?</size></color> Precious is digital life assistant that allows you to interact with your computer 24 hours a day, 7 days in a week. Just tell it to find content, get answers, play music, and connect with friends and friends. It works seamlessly with many popular desktops applications and has very friendly disposition.
